OL,3,COwner tried to castrate XL bully in
OL,4,Cpanic over ban
OL,6,FA dog owner who tried to castrate his
OL,7,FXL bully after the breed was banned
OL,8,Fhas avoided an immediate prison
OL,9,Fsentence.
OL,11,FElliott Arnold, 31 from Hull, admitted
OL,12,Fhe was a "fool" for attempting the
OL,13,Fprocedure using elastic bands,
OL,14,Fthinking that it would save the animal
OL,15,Ffrom being seized and destroyed.
OL,17,FThe dog, called Frank, was left with
OL,18,Flife-threatening injuries.
