OL,6,FHull Crown Court heard Arnold had
OL,7,Ftaken it to a vets after attempting to
OL,8,Fneuter it at home.
OL,10,FOliver Shipley, prosecuting, said:
OL,11,F"The defendant was advised by the
OL,12,Fveterinary staff that Frank was in a
OL,13,Fvery serious and life-threatening
OL,14,Fcondition and would require surgery.
