OL,3,COwner tried to castrate XL bully in
OL,4,Cpanic over ban
OL,6,F"Frank was treated and, fortunately,
OL,7,Fhe survived the ordeal. Both the nurse
OL,8,Fand the surgeon were of the view that
OL,9,FFrank suffered with traumatic pain,
OL,10,Fwhich could have caused sepsis if it
OL,11,Fhad been left untreated, leading to
OL,12,Fdeath.
OL,14,F"She had never seen anything like it
OL,15,Fin her 20 years as a veterinary
OL,16,Fsurgeon."
OL,18,FArnold had watched YouTube videos
OL,19,Fabout how to castrate dogs in the run-
OL,20,Fup to the botched procedure but told
OL,21,Fthe court he was "not a savage."
