OL,3,COwner tried to castrate XL bully in
OL,4,Cpanic over ban
OL,6,FHe said: "I can't bear to relive it. I
OL,7,Fhave shame and regret about it. I have
OL,8,Fnever wanted to hide my actions.
OL,9,FWrongly or stupidly, I acted out of
OL,10,Ffear.
OL,12,F"I have never been in trouble before.
OL,13,FIt's my first ever conviction. I just
OL,14,Fmade a terrible mistake. I thought he
OL,15,Fwas going to be put down and marked as
OL,16,Fa dangerous breed. I feared that he
OL,17,Fwas going to be euthanised."
