OL,3,COwner tried to castrate XL bully in
OL,4,Cpanic over ban
OL,6,FArnold said of his attempt to castrate
OL,7,Fthe dog: "I believed that I could
OL,8,Fsafely do it myself at home. It was a
OL,9,Fmistake.
OL,11,F"Frank was genuinely in no visible
OL,12,Fdistress. I may be a fool but I'm not
OL,13,Fa savage. I have had dogs all my life."
OL,15,FThe judge Mark Bury said that Arnold
OL,16,Fhad been "incredibly stupid", but
OL,17,Faccepted that he did not mean to harm
OL,18,Fthe animal.
