OL,6,FArnold was found guilty of causing
OL,7,Funnecessary suffering to a dog at Hull
OL,8,FCrown Court last September.
OL,10,FHe was handed a 24-week suspended
OL,11,Fprison sentence and he was ordered to
OL,12,Fpay #500 costs. No ban was made on him
OL,13,Fkeeping animals because the incident
OL,14,Fwas a one-off.
